'''异丙醇钛'''、'''四异丙醇钛'''是[[钛|钛]](IV)的[[异丙醇|异丙醇]][[醇盐|盐]]，[[化学式|化学式]]为Ti{OCH(CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>}<sub>4</sub>，用于[[有机合成|有机合成]]和[[材料科学|材料科学]]中。

异丙醇钛结构复杂。晶态时，异丙醇钛为四聚体，分子式为Ti<sub>4</sub>(OCH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>16</sub>。<ref>Wright D. A.; Williams, D. A. “The Crystal and Molecular Structure of Titanium Tetramethoxide” Acta Crystallographica 1968, Volume B24, pages 1107-1114. {{doi|10.1107/S0567740868003766}}</ref>非极性溶剂中不聚合，<ref>Bradley, D. C.; Mehrotra, R.; Rothwell, I.; Singh, A. “Alkoxo and Aryloxo Derivatives of Metals” Academic Press, San Diego, 2001. ISBN 0121241408.</ref>为四面体型[[反磁性|反磁性]]分子。

==制备==
异丙醇钛可由[[四氯化钛|四氯化钛]]和[[异丙醇|异丙醇]]反应制得，副产物为[[氯化氢|氯化氢]]：
:[[四氯化钛|TiCl<sub>4</sub>]]  +  4 (CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>CHOH  →  Ti{OCH(CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>}<sub>4</sub>  +  4 HCl

==性质==
异丙醇钛水解生成[[二氧化钛|二氧化钛]]：
:Ti{OCH(CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>}<sub>4</sub>  +  2 H<sub>2</sub>O  →  TiO<sub>2</sub>  +  4 (CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>CHOH
该反应是[[溶胶-凝胶|溶胶-凝胶]]法合成含TiO<sub>2</sub>材料的基础。产物的特性由添加剂（如[[乙酸|乙酸]]）、加水的量以及混合速度决定 <ref>{{cite journal| last1 = Hanaor| first1 = D.A.H.| last2 = Chironi| first2 = I.| last3 = Karatchevtseva| first3 = I.| last4 = Triani| first4 = G.| last5 = Sorrell| first5 = C.C.| title = Single and Mixed Phase TiO<sub>2</sub> Powders Prepared by Excess Hydrolysis of Titanium Alkoxide| journal = Advances in Applied Ceramics| year = 2012| volume = 111| issue = 3| pages = 149–158| url = https://www.researchgate.net/publication/235644645_Single_and_mixed_phase_TiO_2_powders_prepared_by_excess_hydrolysis_of_titanium_alkoxide| doi = 10.1179/1743676111Y.0000000059| access-date = 2015-10-25| archive-date = 2021-04-24| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210424110337/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/235644645_Single_and_mixed_phase_TiO_2_powders_prepared_by_excess_hydrolysis_of_titanium_alkoxide| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

异丙醇钛用作[[Sharpless不对称环氧化反应|Sharpless不对称环氧化反应]]中的[[路易斯鹼|路易斯鹼]]、[[Kulinkovich反应|Kulinkovich反应]]制备[[环丙烷|三元环]]的催化剂，以及合成前手性[[硫醚|硫醚]]立体选择性氧化时所用的异丙醇钛衍生物催化剂。<ref>S. H. Zhao, O. Samuel, [[Henri_B._Kagan|H. B. Kagan]] “Enantioelective Oxidation of a Sulfide:: (S)-(-)-Methyl p-Tolyl Sulfoxide” Organic Syntheses, Collected Volume 8, p.464 (1993).http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/pdfs/CV8P0464.pdf</ref>

